{{Infobox Professor|name=Georg Kohler|birth_date=1945|birth_place=Konolfingen, Switzerland|citizenship=Swiss|fields=Political philosophy|alma_mater=[[University of Zurich]]|spouse=Dominique Rub|workplaces=Ludwig Maximilian University of Munich University of Zurich}}
'''Georg Kohler''' (born in [[Konolfingen]], Bern, Switzerland in 1945) is a Swiss [[Philosopher]]. He is a professor [[emeritus]] of [[Political philosophy|Political Philosophy]] at [[University of Zurich]]. He is also a publicist and an author. He has written books on political philosophy and modern day Swiss politics and also collaborated with other writers including [[Hermann Lübbe]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.philosophie.uzh.ch/de/seminar/emeriti/kohler.html|title=Georg Kohler|website=www.philosophie.uzh.ch|language=de|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://podium.nzz.ch/person/georg-kohler/|title=Prof. em. Dr. Georg Kohler|work=NZZ Podium|access-date=2017-11-28|language=de-CH}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com.pk/books?id=KWAWBQAAQBAJ&dq=Prof.+em.+Dr.+Georg+Kohler&source=gbs_navlinks_s|title=Politische Kultur in Zeiten des Neoliberalismus: Eine Hegemonieanalyse|last=Maiolino|first=Angelo|date=October 2014|publisher=transcript Verlag|isbn=9783839427606|language=de}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.perlentaucher.de/buch/hermann-luebbe/modernisierungsgewinner.html|title=Hermann Lübbe: Modernisierungsgewinner. Religion, Geschichtssinn, Direkte Demokratie und Moral|access-date=2017-11-28|language=de}}</ref>
Kohler's early education was in grammar schools. He then studied philosophy at the university of Zurich. In 1978 he completed his [[Licentiate (degree)#Switzerland|Licentiate]] degree of [[Jurisprudence|Jurisprudenz]] (law) from the University of Zurich. Until 1980 he held the post of Assistant of Philosophical Seminars at the University but moved away to manage the family business in Vienna. He returned to teaching in 1992 and joined the [[Geschwister-Scholl-Universität|Geschwister Scholl]]-Institute at the University of Munich. He left his post as the chairperson of philosophical research, and joined the University of Zurich in 1994 as a full professor after the retirement of his teacher [[Hermann Lübbe]]. He held the post until 2010, when he became a professor emeritus of Philosophy specializing in Political Philosophy.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.philosophie.uzh.ch/de/seminar/emeriti/kohler.html|title=Georg Kohler|website=www.philosophie.uzh.ch|language=de|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://podium.nzz.ch/person/georg-kohler/|title=Prof. em. Dr. Georg Kohler|work=NZZ Podium|access-date=2017-11-28|language=de-CH}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ruefferundrub.ch/personen/autoren/item/47-kohler|title=rüffer & rub - Autoren - Kohler|website=www.ruefferundrub.ch|language=de-de|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com.pk/books?id=BkEDw74KpNAC&pg=PA45&dq=Georg+Kohler&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwizrviGreHXAhXHQBQKHfbCCXgQ6AEIKjAB#v=onepage&q=Georg%20Kohler&f=false|title=Conflicts and New Departures in World Society|last=Bornschier|first=Volker|last2=Lengyel|first2=Peter|date=1994-01-01|publisher=Transaction Publishers|isbn=9781412820141}}</ref>
Since 2008 he has been a speaker and a member of the trustees with the [[Classical liberalism|classical liberal]] think tank [[Liberales Institut]]. He frequently writes and gives interviews to newspapers and online publications, such as [[Neue Zürcher Zeitung]], [[Blick]] and [[Tages-Anzeiger]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.libinst.ch/?i=veranstaltungen-archiv-vor-2008|title=Liberales Institut - Vergangene Veranstaltungen vor 2008|last=pansay.com|website=www.libinst.ch|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://portal.dnb.de/opac.htm?query=120792524&method=simpleSearch|title=Katalog der Deutschen Nationalbibliothek|website=portal.dnb.de|language=de|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n80-087430/|title=Seven poems /|website=www.worldcat.org|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.blick.ch/suche/?q=Georg%20Kohler|title=Georg Kohler {{!}} Suche {{!}} Blick|last=Blick|website=www.blick.ch|language=de|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nzz.ch/suche?form%5Bq%5D=Georg+Kohler|title=Suchresultate {{!}} NZZ|website=www.nzz.ch|language=de|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tagesanzeiger.ch/service/suche/suche.html?date=alle&order=date&key=Georg+Kohler|title=tagesanzeiger.ch: Nichts verpassen|website=www.tagesanzeiger.ch|access-date=2017-11-28}}</ref>
Kohler was married to [[SRF Tagesschau|Tagesschau]] spokeswoman and journalist Dominique Rub Kohler. She died on 15 August 2013.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.blick.ch/people-tv/mit-60-jahren-ex-tagesschau-sprecherin-dominique-rub-ist-tot-id2413675.html|title=Mit 60 Jahren: Ex-Tagesschau-Sprecherin Dominique Rub ist tot|last=Blick|access-date=2017-11-28|language=de}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.tagesanzeiger.ch/kultur/fernsehen/ExTagesschauSprecherin-Rub-ist-tot/story/27146236|title=Ex-"Tagesschau"-Sprecherin Rub ist tot|date=2013-08-21|work=Tages-Anzeiger, Tages-Anzeiger|access-date=2017-11-28|language=de|issn=1422-9994}}</ref>
